data.description: Subject to Existing Home Sale Contingency.  OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY FEB. 24 FROM 11AM-1PM.  Look no further for a rewarding escape peacefully located just minutes south of Bellevue. This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home is ready for entertaining with the large family room, wetbar with kitchen, walkout basement to the inground pool.  Sitting on 2.57 acres surrounded by mature trees, to allow for privacy while enjoying the outdoors.  A new water heater and roof was completed in 2023 and new pool liner installed in 2022.  An invisible fence encompasses the perimeter of the property line allowing pets to run freely in this spacious backyard.  Master bathroom boasts a whirlpool tub with his and her sinks, skylight and walk in closet.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home.
